Aspect Oriented Programming (AOP)

1 Define aop class annotated with @Aspect annotation
    - @Before
    - @After
    - @Returning
    - @Throwing

tips: value = "execution(METHOD_REFERENCE)"
      returning="result"  -> Object
      throwing="exception" -> Exception
      JointPoint -> to get joint pointer info

2 create bean in configuration or with annotation

3 enable aspectj auto proxy - do not forget this step

4 get bean with application context



